content=["<dl>",
"<dt><a href='#Section0'>Sepsis</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section0'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Can be caused by many different pathogens. There are no differentiating signs and symptoms.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Blood culture may provide the aetiological agent. Other sign/symptom-directed test (i.e., CT abdomen) may provide the source of sepsis.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section1'>Gangrene</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section1'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Can be caused by infection or ischaemia. There are no differentiating signs and symptoms.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Blood culture may provide the aetiological agent.</p>",
"</dd>",
"<dt><a href='#Section2'>Infectious diarrhoea</a></dt>",
"<dd id='Section2'>",
"<p><strong>Sign & Symptoms:</strong> Differential diagnosis is broad, as various bacteria, parasites, and viruses cause diarrhoea. There are no differentiating signs and symptoms.",
"<br><strong>Test:</strong> Presence of specific infectious agent on stool or serological testing.</p>",
"</dd>",
"</dl>"].join("\n");